{"tid":146513,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"155cm郭書瑤被SpeXial以綸拍出逆天美腿 往上一看表情卻崩壞","createTime":"2017-03-07T07:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T07:24:25.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87a938d2557badc2b3825d64bc136f048a704045","tid":146513,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"藝人瑤瑤（郭書瑤）近日忙於拍攝新戲《稍息立正我愛你》，和同劇演員SpeXial成員以綸感情要好，互動逗趣可愛，6日時她就上傳了一張自己的照片，稱讚以綸把自己拍得很瘦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2375/d2375927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2375%2Fd2375927.jpg&h=49c45c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲瑤瑤近日忙於拍攝新戲《稍息立正我愛你》，和同劇演員SpeXial成員以綸感情要好。<br />\n<br />\n瑤瑤6日時上傳一張照片開心地直呼，「幫我拍照的人很善良，因為他把我拍的好瘦喔～～」而掌鏡人就是一起合作新戲的以綸。照片中的她被拍得身高不像只有155公分的模樣，穿著平口衣服露出香肩，盡現女神美麗氣質。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2375/d2375929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2375%2Fd2375929.jpg&h=5c4e4e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲瑤瑤的腿被拍得又細又長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kps0717.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkps0717.jpg&h=6b7c7334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲千雪的腿躺著也比她長。<br />\n<br />\n不過一往上看，卻發現瑤瑤張著嘴巴，似乎是毫無防備的情況下被拍下，連她本人都忍不住說，「但表情就⋯」，並附上一個尷尬汗顏的表情，但其實在粉絲心中仍是「可愛滿分」。另外，以綸發現自己拍的照被稱讚後，還附上戴墨鏡的帥圖回覆，「以後以張數計費 修圖服務另加$2,000」，讓粉絲直呼太貴了，互動逗趣可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2375/2375930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2375%2F2375930.jpg&h=84f40b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼瑤瑤臉書全文和以綸回應。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2375/d2375960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2375%2Fd2375960.jpg&h=1eed0422&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acedfe0ae9fc887faac57bb416a4f9bb294088a1","tid":146513,"uid":15777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"今次有睇user name<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c80efa9c162212ad8401521b3b088327528386f","tid":146513,"uid":86727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"話說近年個樣好似靚咗"}]}